description: Yi Dim Sum is literally translated as "a little touch of the heart." This truck creates a modern interpretation of an authentic dim sum experience in a fun food truck setting for catering and street food celebrations. The menu is based on traceable sources, natural ingredients and is often inspired by the seasons. Visit and enjoy the juicy Shanghai pan-fried soup dumpling, har gau, sui mai, and many more delicious items!
name: Yi Dim Sum
